description: Application for Non-Material amendment to planning permission ref: PA/14/03195, Dated 30/09/2016.Amendments Sought: To reduce the extent of basement and the number of car parking spaces as follows: Reduction of Phase 1 car park to a single-storey basement depth; Reduction in overall car parking spaces from 244 to 194 across both Phases; and Realignment of basement walls.
site_name: Two Sites: SITE 1 Land at 3 Millharbour and SITE 2 land at 6, 7 and 8 South Quay Square, South Quay Square, London
